These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, argentine, turkish
1. the turkish is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the turkish is between the nigerian and the argentine##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | turkish | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, action, crime
1. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching action movies and the person watching crime movies##2
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | spy | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, jazz, disco
1. the fan of jazz is between the fan of rock and the fan of disco##2
2. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | jazz | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: fish, bird, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up, lemonade
1. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking 7up##2
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | 7up | mirinda | lemonade |

 #################################

 
